{"tid":2351195,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 有人不滿國會未有通過疫情援助金增至2,000美元 美國參眾兩院領袖住宅遭人破壞","createTime":"2021-01-03T04:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T07:34:27.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14996315b4a67c3a86415d1701f3f6f8332d3c04","tid":2351195,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"美國參眾兩院領袖的住宅先後遭人塗鴉破壞。  <br />\n<br />\n共和黨的參議院領袖麥康奈爾位於肯塔基州的住所，周六外牆被人塗鴉，信箱亦寫上詛咒麥康奈爾的字句。麥康奈爾發聲明譴責。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主黨籍眾議院議長佩洛西亦遭殃，她在加州三藩市的住所元旦亦遭人破壞。工作人員用黑膠布遮蓋車房門被塗污部分。  <br />\n<br />\n警方透露有人噴上塗鴉，甚至留下豬頭和假血。初步懷疑有人不滿國會未有通過一次過向每名國民發放的疫情援助金由600美元，增至2,000美元，而干犯刑毀罪行洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5ff102b334b031c865f3b797/美國參眾兩院領袖住宅先後遭人塗鴉破壞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5ff102b334b031c865f3b797%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%83%E7%9C%BE%E5%85%A9%E9%99%A2%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%85%88%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%A1%97%E9%B4%89%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0FFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=22165944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5ff102b334b031c865f3b797/美國參眾兩院領袖住宅先後遭人塗鴉破壞</a>"},{"pid":"bb16037109b281d043e2f4d26695821360003359","tid":2351195,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f34c2cb8d73291195d8576ba8b9bce69805653e","tid":2351195,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"香港都試過去紅官間屋附近寫大字"},{"pid":"150b8ab588ec8e6e6763d30f63424341c395ea91","tid":2351195,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0